OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRishi Sunak vows to cut VAT
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fon energy in campaign shift
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Tory leadership hopeful Rishi Sunak has
OL,6, pledged to scrap the 5% VAT rate on    
OL,7, household energy bills if prices       
OL,8, continue to rise later this year.      
OL,10,FThe former chancellor, who has not     
OL,11,Fpromised tax cuts so far in his        
OL,12,Fcampaign, said the plan would help     
OL,13,Ffamilies with rising living costs.     
OL,15,FRival Liz Truss's campaign team        
OL,16,Fdescribed the move as desperate -      
OL,17,Faccusing him of a "screeching U-turn". 
OL,19,FMeanwhile rival Ms Truss has pledged to
OL,20,Fcut key crime rates if she wins.       
